T1  - Optimal contract for asset trades: Collateralizing or selling?
AU  - Kang, Kee-Youn
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 56
SP  - 100590
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/11/01/
SN  - 1386-4181
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1016/j.finmar.2020.100590
